General.Name: MUI Properties Bhd
General.Description: MUI Properties Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in property development business in Malaysia. It operates through two segments, Properties and Investment Holding. The company develops and sells residential and commercial properties; and invests in properties. It is also involved in the operation of petrol stations; sale of oil palm fruits; and trading of petroleum products. The company was incorporated in 1965 and is based in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. MUI Properties Berhad is a subsidiary of Malayan United Industries Berhad.
